>Billing information and outstanding accounts</li>\r\n	<li>Booking history</li>\r\n	<li>Tab account balances and top up</li>\r\n</ul>','MEMBERSHIP MANAGEMENT','','publish','closed','closed','','membership-management','','','2015-09-03 11:00:56','2015-09-03 10:00:56','',0,'http://itee:8888/?post_type=home_clusters&#038;p=64',1,'home_clusters','',0),(65,1,'2015-06-19 13:45:13','2015-06-19 13:45:13','MOBILE POINT OF SALES INTEGRATES ALL SHOPS INCLUDING ON COURSE CART\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Full shop set up</li>\r\n	<li>Includes Pro Shop and rental purchases</li>\r\n	<li>Secure payment process</li>\r\n	<li>Can set promotion items</li>\r\n	<li>Flexible discount structure</li>\r\n</ul>','POINT OF SALE','','publish','closed','closed','','point-of-sale','','','2015-09-03 11:02:14','2015-09-03 10:02:14','',0,'http://itee:8888/?post_type=home_clusters&#038;p=65',2,'home_clusters','',0),(66,1,'2015-06-19 13:46:08','2015-06-19 13:46:08','GIVE YOUR TOURNAMENTS A PROFESSIONAL EVENT FEEL\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>A dedicated application for all tournament management requirements</li>\r\n	<li>Entry procedures</li>\r\n	<li>Secure Entry Fee payment</li>\r\n	<li>Publishing of tee time draw</li>\r\n	<li>Electronic scorecard</li>\r\n</ul>','COMPETITION MANAGEMENT','','publish','closed','closed','','competition-management','','','2015-09-03 11:02:41','2015-09-03 10:02:41','',0,'http://itee:8888/?post_type=home_clusters&#038;p=66',3,'home_clusters','',0),(67,1,'2015-06-19 13:46:56','2015-06-19 13:46:56','USE THE NEW MOBILE SETUP TO ENGAGE WITH YOUR CUSTOMERS\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>System includes a customer specific app for Android and iPhone</li>\r\n	<li>Allows members and visitors to book tee times in real time</li>\r\n	<li>Gives club full control over available times and pricing</li>\r\n	<li>Members can enter events and view results</li>\r\n</ul>','CUSTOMER APP','','publish','closed','closed','','customer-app','','','2015-09-03 13:52:30','2015-09-03 12:52:30','',0,'http://itee:8888/?post_type=home_clusters&#0