>\r\n	<li>Secure payment process</li>\r\n	<li>Can set promotion items</li>\r\n	<li>Flexible discount structure</li>\r\n	<li>Perfect for management of sales at the drinks cart and halfway house</li>\r\n	<li>Pin and Signature verification</li>\r\n	<li>Accepts different payment types by transfer to tab accounts or cash, credit card or voucher payments</li>\r\n	<li>Allows splitting of the bill</li>\r\n	<li>Refund processing</li>\r\n</ul>','Point of Sales','','publish','closed','closed','','point-of-sales','','','2015-07-20 13:55:37','2015-07-20 12:55:37','',0,'http://iteesystems.com/?post_type=features&#038;p=116',2,'features','',0),(117,1,'2015-07-20 13:07:25','2015-07-20 12:07:25','<ul>\r\n	<li>A dedicated application for all tournament management requirements</li>\r\n	<li>Entry procedures</li>\r\n	<li>Secure Entry Fee payment</li>\r\n	<li>Publishing of tee time draw</li>\r\n	<li>Electronic scorecard</li>\r\n	<li>Big Screen Scoring at the clubhouse</li>\r\n	<li>Final results publication</li>\r\n	<li>Export of scores in various formats to add to handicapping system.</li>\r\n</ul>','Competition Management','','publish','closed','closed','','competition-management','','','2015-07-20 13:56:28','2015-07-20 12:56:28','',0,'http://iteesystems.com/?post_type=features&#038;p=117',3,'features','',0),(118,1,'2015-07-20 13:07:54','2015-07-20 12:07:54','<ul>\r\n	<li>System includes a customer specific app for android and iPhone.</li>\r\n	<li>Allows members and Visitors to book tee times in real time</li>\r\n	<li>Gives club full control over available times and pricing</li>\r\n	<li>Members can enter events and view results</li>\r\n	<li>Members can see the account information and top up their tab accounts.</li>\r\n	<li>App fully customised with golf club logo</li>\r\n	<li>Includes electronic scoring facility and tracks statistics</li>\r\n	<li>Gives up to date news from the club</li>\r\n	<li>Chat facility between your playing partners and friends</li>\r\n</ul>','Customer app','','publish','closed','closed','','customer-app','','','2015-07-20 13:57:09','2015-07-20 12:57:09','',0,'http://iteesystems.com/?post_type=features&#038;p=118',4,'features','',0),(119,1,'2015-07-20 14:17:50','2015-07-20 13:17:50','','Technologies','','publish','closed','closed','','technologies','','','2015-07-20 14:28:11','2015-07-20 13:28:11','',0,'http://iteesystems.com/?post_type=accordions&#038;p=119',0,'accordions','',0),(124,3,'2015-09-01 11:58:41','2015-09-01 10:58:41','iTee Systems has developed a fully integrated application that will fulfil all your golf club management and operation requirements. The application can be installed into any mobile device giving you freedom to carry out your day-to-day business from any location. No longer will you need to be stationary at your workspace.','About iTee Systems','','inherit','closed','closed','','70-autosave-v1','','','2015-09-01 11:58:41','2015-09-01 10:58:41','',70,'http://iteesystems.com/70-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(125,3,'2015-09-01 11:59:34','2015-09-01 10:59:34','iTee Systems has developed a fully integrated application that will fulfil all your golf club management and operation requirements. The application can be installed into any mobile device giving you freedom to carry out your day-to-day business from any location. No longer will you need to be stationary at your workspace.','About iTee Systems','','inherit','closed','closed','','70-revision-v1','','','2015-09-01 11:59:34','2015-09-01 10:59:34','',70,'http://iteesystems.com/70-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(126,3,'2015-09-01 12:16:27','2015-09-01 11:16:27','This new set up for your club management system gives you the flexibility to manage your club more efficiently, increases opportunity for additional revenue, enhance customer services and cost saving from a mobile workforce.\r\n\r\nA number of additional applications integrated into the main system gives the clubs the ability to engage with the customers, manage tournaments and live scoring features and provide Agents a direct booking platform.','Features','','inherit','closed','closed','','7-autosave-v1','','','2015-09-01 12:16:27','2015-09-01 11:16:27','',7,'http://iteesystems.com/7-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(128,3,'2015-09-01 12:42:12','2015-09-01 11:42:12','iTee Systems was founded with the mission to give freedom to golf clubs by providing the golf course management system as an application. Giving the clubs the opportunity to use latest technology to modernise their business model.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','About us','','inherit','closed','closed','','15-autosave-v1','','','2015-09-01 12:42:12','2015-09-01 11:42:12','',15,'http://iteesystems.com/15-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(130,3,'2015-09-01 12:46:34','2015-09-01 11:46:34','If you’d like to talk to someone at iTee about our products and how it can be integrated into your club management system please call (44) 01494 68 18 67.','Contact','','inherit','closed','closed','','17-autosave-v1','','','2015-09-01 12:46:34','2015-09-01 11:46:34','',17,'http://iteesystems.com/17-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(131,3,'2015-09-01 12:46:48','2015-09-01 11:46:48','If you’d like to talk to someone at iTee about our products and how it can be integrated into your club management system please call (44) 01494 68 18 67.','Contact','','inherit','closed','closed','','17-revision-v1','','','2015-09-01 12:46:48','2015-09-01 11:46:48','',17,'http://iteesystems.com/17-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
